title: Mr Boukadoum holds phone talks with American counterpart
text: Minister of Foreign Affairs, Mr Sabri Boukadoum, held on Thursday April 29th, 2021, phone talks with US Secretary of State, Mr Antony Blinken, on ways to strengthen strategic partnership between Algeria and the United States of America in various fields.
The two sides also exchange views on regional issues of common interest, notably the situation in Western Sahara, Mali and in Libya.
